{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2019-02/CSS-블록-지정-색","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"GyeongSu Han's Github Pages","author":"@micalgenus","siteUrl":"https://micalgenus.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"144638de-0287-503e-9c37-056fcf55c6d0","html":"<p>텍스트를 드래그 했을 때 기본적으로 파란 배경에 하얀 글씨로 변경된다.</p>\n<p>이 효과를 변경하기 위해서는 <code class=\"language-text\">-moz-selection</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">selection</code>선택자를 사용하여 변경할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>기본적인 CSS이기 때문에 글자 효과 말고 다른 효과도 줄 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Code for Firefox */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">::-moz-selection</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">::selection</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"categories":["Web"],"title":"CSS 블록 지정 색","date":"Feb 20, 2019","tags":["CSS"]}}},"pageContext":{"comments":true,"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-02/swap-파일-추가","title":"Linux swap 파일 추가","comments":true}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-02/Safari-zindex-문제","title":"Safari zindex 문제","comments":true}}}}}